<br>
Her strength is already high enough to get high avg and max damage from the weapons she has. And, with the damage caps lower levels are penalized with, increasing her strength probably wont help much anyways.<br>
<br>
The same is true for her dex.. which is very important in the lower levels to insure that weapons skills increase at a steady rate.  Increasing her dex past its current level of 168 would probably not make a significant contribution.<br>
<br>
The relative importance of a stat is highly situational and not answered with cookie-cutter formulas that state a>b>c. At one level a character may need ac/hp, and at another str/dex and then at yet another level (when raiding for example) resists.<br>
<br>
Her character seems to have all the bases well covered, altho i would try to get agi up another 8-10 points. Having agi high enough to prevent loss of ac and "deathstep" when health drops very low and can make the difference between life and death.<br>
<br>
To answer her original question, Tattered Mantle is an excellent item for her.. and they fit within her budget. :)<br>
